text: Maryam baxi Nabii Qiisa tamah keenik oggoleeh isi Rabbi kallacak Yallaw Ni-Rabbow Qaraanak maaqoy nee kee nek ellecabo marah Qid takkeeh kok tan Astay atu inki Rabbi kinnitooh anu ku-farmoyta kinniyoomuh Sumaq takke nel oobis, atu Rizqhi neh Acuy atu Rizqhi yacee marak kayrih yayse Rabbi kinnitok iyye
